+ *             EDP_BACKLIGHT_FREQ_SET register (DPCD Address 00728h)
+ * - Where P = 2^Pn, where Pn is the value programmed by field 4:0 of the
+ *             EDP_PWMGEN_BIT_COUNT register (DPCD Address 00724h)
+ */
